<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>7213</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>13039</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一天，一个叫汉斯的小男孩儿走路去朋友家。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>13041</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>15906</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>天气寒冷，还刮着风。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>15907</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20899</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是汉斯想给他的朋友带点儿热蛋糕。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20900</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27869</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汉斯生活在荷兰，那里的大坝为陆地挡住了海水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27870</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31534</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>陆地被用来种植小麦。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31535</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37187</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>村民们在镇子和田地周围砌上了砖墙。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37188</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40675</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这些砖墙被称为大坝。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40676</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44102</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大坝防止田地被淹没。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44103</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51510</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当天气变得风雨交加时，汉斯正从朋友家往回赶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51511</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56190</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>风吹着他的脸颊，也吹乱了他的围巾。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56191</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61280</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，汉斯看到大坝上有个洞。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61281</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68325</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他知道那个洞很危险，因为它会变得越来越大。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68326</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74698</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果洞变得太大，海水可能会淹没城镇。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74699</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79777</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>庄稼会被毁掉，村民们会挨饿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79778</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86174</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汉斯不知道该怎么办，于是他跑去寻求帮助。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86175</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88721</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>风吹得很猛烈。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88722</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95097</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他大声喊叫，但是因为风太大，没人能听得到。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95098</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98882</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他不得不自己解决这个问题。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98883</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101660</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汉斯回到大坝。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101661</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105796</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，我该怎么做？”他心想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105797</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108681</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我只是一个小男孩儿！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108682</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>111455</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>终于，他有了主意。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>111456</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>117490</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他把围巾缠在手上然后把拳头塞进洞里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>117491</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121054</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这阻止了水继续渗透大坝。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121055</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124275</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>风雨夜是那么漫长。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124276</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128123</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我必须变得强大。”汉斯心想，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128124</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131666</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我必须像一个男人一样勇敢。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131667</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134087</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汉斯疲倦了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134088</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139920</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我好累，但是我必须阻止海水。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139921</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>144834</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>早晨终于来临，风暴也平息了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>144835</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149404</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个老人发现了手还在大坝里的汉斯。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149405</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153401</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他正在发抖，快要被冻死了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153402</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157375</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汉斯堵了一整夜。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157376</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161111</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>镇子上的砖匠跑来修复大坝。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161112</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>167007</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汉斯抽出他的拳头，他们迅速封堵住了洞口。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>167008</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170673</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汉斯被裹上暖和的大衣。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170674</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176796</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他很累，但是依然在温暖的晨光中微笑着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176797</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>180939</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>风暴过去了，小镇安全了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>180940</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187230</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的妈妈和全镇村民都为汉斯感到非常骄傲。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187231</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194476</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天，一个明亮的早晨，镇上为表扬汉斯的壮举，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194477</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>196301</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>授予了他奖章。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>196302</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>209869</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>从那时起，汉斯作为“有大勇气的荷兰小男孩儿”家喻户晓。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>